data.description: Natures Wonderland ! This well maintained/updated 3bed/3bath gambrel style home is situated on 1.8 beautiful acres with a gate on lower end of parcel that leads directly to trails going to national forests. Located close to Jenkinson Lake this house has a comfortable welcoming and spacious floorplan (great for entertaining), wrap around deck and modern amenities, high speed internet, accent lights, cherry/oak wood floors etc. Need more room ? no problem, enjoy a 900sqft basement with outside access and many possibilities. There is a nice spot for reserved for RV's plus various other useable areas of parcel make this one a must have'. Enjoy equestrian, hiking, boating, fishing, mountain biking everything outdoor lovers crave within walking distance.
